item.title: What's This All About?
item.description: Intro I have always been interested in things… many things. My mind is a constant torrent of ideas, questions, “hmm” thoughts. These often lead me on multi-hour research journeys. While learning many things can often seem like a good thing, it only is if you remember what you learned 2 or 3 days later. Due to this, note taking has become a big part of my life, at least for the things I’m planning to remember days, months, or years later.
